column5: The Indian premium/discount data is sourced from NCDEX (one of the commodity exchanges in India), which started publishing this data from 21 May 2015. Prior to that, premium/discount was calculated using the 'Premia Sheet-Old' worksheet. More information can be found in the accompanying metholdogy note. *Polled Premium for 995 Gold at Ahmedabad in USD/troy oz.

column1: Source: MCX; RBI; NCDEX; World Gold Council
